ain’s ‘drink problem’.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aAlcoholxLaw and legislation. 0aAlcoholxSocial aspectsxHistoryy20th centuryzEngland. 0aAlcoholxSocial aspectsxHistoryy20th centuryzWales. 0aDrinking of alcoholic beveragesxHistoryy20th centuryzEngland. 0aDrinking of alcoholic beveragesxHistoryy20th centuryzWales. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Criminology.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783111196343oZDB-23-BUPP40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447309949423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447309949/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-BUPPb2014